cat << EOF
Epoz allows you to edit Zope- or Plone-objects with a wysiwyg-editor. No plugins
are required. You only have to use a recent browser (IE >= 5.5, Mozilla >= 1.3.1)
that supports Rich-Text-controls (called Midas for Mozilla).
EOF
